{"word":"G4350 - προσκόπτω - proskóptō - pros-kop'-to - Beat upon","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προσκόπτω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">proskóptō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pros-kop'-to</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Beat upon</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - இடறு, மோது"},{"paragraph":"to strike against, to stumble"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4314 - πρός - prós - pros/4314\">G4314</a> and <a href=\"#/G2875 - κόπτω - kóptō - kop'-to/2875\">G2875</a>; to <i>strike at</i>, that is, <i>surge against</i> (as water); specifically to <i>stub on</i>, that is, <i>trip up</i> (literally or figuratively): - beat upon, dash, stumble (at).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4348/4348\">G4348</a>, <a href=\"#/G4349/4349\">G4349</a>, <a href=\"#/G4350/4350\">G4350</a>, <a href=\"#/G677/677\">G677</a>"}]}